records.addlTxt:
The State files an Amended Information which charges one count of harrassment, contrary to Section 947.013(1r) of the Wisconsin Statutes.
NO CONTEST plea entered to the amended charge.  Convicted.
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is palced on probation to DOC for twelve (12) months.
Conditions of probation:
1) maintain fulltime work, school or a combination;
2) assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
3) pay court costs;
4) perform thirty (30) hours of community service with service performed in Waupaca County allowed;
5) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Minutes.
